reviewText: Very good package; however, there is duplication from other volumes.
This was a favourite of mine as a child and have enjoyed watching the DVD.

Dick Jones as "Buffalo Bill Jr." delivers his fights and stunts with gusto with help from his sister Calamity. Don't expect Gunsmoke-like plots, though. This is a TV western for KIDS of all ages. The DVD features the first episode ever and the four episodes in volume 1 have a good video transfer in my opinion.
